wards slightly before striking. Enemies hit by this jab are stunned for 1s. 80 Energy: King Arthur charges forward with Excalibur drawn. If King Arthur hits an enemy god, he launches them into the air and unleashes a barrage of 6 attacks, after which he launches them back to the ground dealing damage to the target and any enemy below.", :ability4_cooldown=>"20", :ability4_id=>16637, :ability4_type=>"Line (Dash)", :ability4_image=>"https://web2.hirez.com/smite/god-abilities/sundering-strike.jpg"}, 
